What you need to know:

The 31-year-old Harden finished with 32 points, 14 assists and 12 rebounds in his debut with the Nets, who will have to wait a little longer to show off their new Big Three of Harden, Durant and Kyrie IrvingHarden, who became the first player in history to record a 30-point triple double in their debut for a new club, slammed the door on his way out of Houston after a four-team trade deal was completedDeMar DeRozan scored 24 points and the San Antonio Spurs rolled over the Rockets 103-91 in the second game between the teams over a three-day span